dct_title_s: [Kharitat al-Iraq]: shu'bat al-Mahmudiyah wa nahiyat al-Iskandariyah
dct_description_sm: Iraq. Mudiriyat ar-Rayy al-Ammah Shu'bat al-Misaha. Iraq. General Directorate of Irrigation. Surveying Division. [[Map of Iraq]: Iskandariyah county and Mahmudiyah district. Alternate title: Liwa' Baghdad wa al-Hillah: Qada'ay al-Mahmudiyah wa al-Musayyab: Shu'bat al-Mahmudiya wa Nahiyat al-Iskandariyah. [Baghdad and al-Hillah provinces: Mahmudiyah and al-Musayyab districts: al-Mahmudiya district and Iskandariya county.] Relief shown by hachures and form lines. Triangulation points are shown. Surveyed: 1934. Tribal lands and ownership are shown.
